Summary: Formal limits

Below we include 2 types of summary of Formal limits, a graphical summary and a table summary with all the cases per instrument.

Graphical Data Summary

The Formal Limits scale has been constructed on the basis:

  • 35 Does the proposal have to be submitted as a (draft) legal text?

  • 37 Is there a clarity of the question requirement?

  • 38 Is there a unity of form requirement?

  • 39 Is there a unity of substance requirement?

Note: for the Law-initiated, item 35 was not used.
